Title: Zindagi Ke Pal

Zindagi ek safar hai, jisme har mod pe kuch naya seekhne ko milta hai.  
Kabhi hansna padta hai, toh kabhi aansu bhi aate hain.  
Par yeh yaadein hi toh humein insan banati hain.

Subah ki chai ke saath maa ki daant,  
Aur shaam ko dosto ke saath ki woh hasi mazaak.  
Har din kuch khaas hota hai, bas humein dekhne ki nazar chahiye.

Zindagi chhoti hai, par isme lamhe bade hote hain.  
Isliye har pal ko jeeyo, muskurate hue,  
Kyuki kal kisne dekha hai?

- Author: Aam Aadmi
